From 22d4733acb9c4485564a4436b55ab0ce3c333ea4 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Artem Goncharov <artem.goncharov@gmail.com>
Date: Mon, 1 Jul 2024 20:24:36 +0200
Subject: [PATCH 1008/1026] Enable JsonSchema validation for `project`

Add JsonSchema validation for `project` resource.

- extend schemas
- remove lazy validation in the code
- allow `False`/`True` as query parameters (is_domain test explicitly
  validates those are valid so it is inconsistent to forbid those. This
  also matches behavior of other services.

Change-Id: Icc74d6356494d77f044236c508260eddb8728c6a
(cherry picked from commit 5cf620a088b5e5d97f5eff01f797a8e2c8eb81dc)
